 &lt;h2 id="auto-completion">
 Auto Completion
 &lt;a data-clipboard-text="https://csmertx.github.io/Linux/Shells/bash/#auto-completion" class="gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip" aria-label="Anchor Auto Completion" href="#auto-completion">
