&lt;div class="gdoc-page__anchorwrap">
 &lt;h3 id="add-pause-to-zshrc">
 Add Pause to ~/.zshrc
 &lt;a data-clipboard-text="https://csmertx.github.io/Linux/Shells/zsh/#add-pause-to-zshrc" class="gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip" aria-label="Anchor Add Pause to ~/.zshrc" href="#add-pause-to-zshrc">
 &lt;svg class="icon gdoc_link">&lt;use xlink:href="#gdoc_link">&lt;/use>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
 &lt;/h3>
&lt;/div>&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code># Enable pause
# Uses: pause;command
function pause(){
 echo &amp;#34;Press [Enter] to continue...&amp;#34;;grep $1 2&amp;gt;/dev/null;read
}
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Example: &lt;code>pause; echo &amp;quot;Pause Complete&amp;quot;&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>I use this in conjunction with &lt;a class="gdoc-markdown__link" href="../../Linux/Software/tmux">Tmux&lt;/a> helper &lt;a class="gdoc-markdown__link" href="https://github.com/tmuxinator/tmuxinator">Tmuxinator&lt;/a>, so that STDOUT renders out everything correctly&lt;/p>
